---
title: Glazed Chicken and Bell Peppers with green peas and rice
description: Ketjap manis—also known as Indonesian ketchup—is a popular Asian condiment similar to soy sauce, but sweeter. It forms the base of the syrupy, tangy glaze coating the succulent chicken and veg in this delicious dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R16_W46_IE_IEXCLC0050-15__Main_rice_edit_high-be1e3402.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/6602dc2faa3c1e8a857471da.pdf
